# Windsurf — UI design only

Apply **only** when designing, styling, or building visual UI.

## Activation

- User requests design system, styling, or layout/visual changes
- Files: `_sass/**`, `_includes/**`, `_layouts/**`, `assets/css/**`, `index.html`, `design/**`

## Do not apply

Config, content-only, analytics, or non-visual code paths.

## Source of truth

`design/design-system.md`

## Stack

Jekyll + SCSS + HTML includes. Tokens → SCSS variables in `_sass/`; preserve existing skin/partial structure.

## Constraints

Wobbly borders, hard offset shadows, hand-drawn palette and fonts, rotation and dashed accents, responsive decorative hiding, 48px touch targets. See design doc for component patterns (buttons, cards, inputs).
